<s> Crown Resources Corp. said it reached a definitive agreement to acquire the Gold Texas Resources Ltd. shares it does n't already own . </s>
<s> Under the proposed agreement , Gold Texas holders will receive 1.43 Crown shares for each of the 1.1 million Gold Texas shares not owned by Crown , which already owns 65 % . </s>
<s> The arrangement is subject to approval by the Supreme Court of British Columbia province , Crown said . </s>
<s> Gold Texas is based in Vancouver , British Columbia , and Crown Resources is based in Denver . </s>
<s> Both are mining concerns . </s>
